Package: QuantFit
Title: Latent Structure Model Selection Framework
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("QuantFit Authors", email = "quantfit@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the model selection framework from Torres Irribarra &
    Diakow's paper "Categorization, Ordering and Quantification: Selecting a
    Latent Variable Model by Comparing Latent Structures." Enables researchers
    to compare six latent structure models (Unconstrained Latent Class, Class
    Monotonicity, Invariant Item Ordering, Double Monotonicity, Latent Class
    Rasch, and Rasch Model) to determine whether data supports classificatory,
    ordinal, or quantitative interpretations of a latent variable.
